{"tid":461057,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【過程超驚險】雷神澳洲客串墮馬！明晚快活谷未知能否上陣","createTime":"2017-11-07T08:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T09:04:33.000Z","uid":525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"165ab9502372faf65e4535755c26a605922c5c0a","tid":461057,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"本港冠軍騎師雷神莫雷拉今日（7日）於澳洲費明頓馬場客串一日，惟在當地第四場2800米賽事中(此場本港沒有受注)，策騎Regal Monarch途中墮馬，無法繼續當地餘下賽事策騎，包括重頭戲墨爾本盃座騎「何必選擇」亦已換人。<br />\n<br />\n雷神墮馬後不久，駐場醫護人員已立即迅速前往他落樓之處，雷神聲稱雙腳感到痛楚，救護人員即時給他自行吸服止痛噴劑，在醫護人員攙扶下，雷神能站起來，之後自己還可以緩步至救護車，回到觀眾席時，更向當地馬迷舉起手指公，表示自己沒事。<br />\n<br />\n雖然墮馬倒地一刻，莫雷拉疑被馬匹踩中，但從上述舉動看來，似乎他傷勢不算太重；Regal Monarch亦能自行步上運馬車，至馬醫院接受進一步檢查。<br />\n<br />\n雷神於墨爾本盃（一級賽3200米）的座騎「何必選擇」，已換上澳洲騎師艾朗（Ben Allen）上陣，結果落第而回。<br />\n<br />\n雷神將趕回港，但周三晚（8日）快活谷馬場夜賽他能否上陣，仍是未知之數，一切仍要等馬會周三上午公佈。而他周三晚共7匹座騎，均已設後備騎師<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20171107/57427935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57427935&d=uRLXyxrl2rCmh2DUqYmbWoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=4ee80542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57427935&h=61c040eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20171107/57427935</a><br />\n馬都係有靈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd0ab1c005561775f781c0e6af65ec51c2142e7","tid":461057,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:15:24.000Z","msg":"雷神之前有無騎過melbourne cup"},{"pid":"c6fd4c7cc37355ca38568b18bf2d4d949a2700a8","tid":461057,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雷神之前有無騎過melbourne cup</blockquote><br />\n有<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2016-10/news_2016102701723.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fcorporate%2Fracing_news_item.asp%3Fin_file%3D%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2016-10%2Fnews_2016102701723.html&d=uRLXyxrl2rCmh2DUqYmbWoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=cf66ecda\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2016-10/news_2016102701723.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a60e4ca9ecbd41222dae25588f8559bcd7e35b5","tid":461057,"uid":525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"d馬踩大力d嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66824d63075fa52953f06d0520bed223be94dc6","tid":461057,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"點解死唔去"},{"pid":"be51a7233a7d1a8f366b02cbdf2811cde0539931","tid":461057,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"第一次騎師墮馬都咁開心，<br />\n死左幾隻馬係時候同佢索命！"},{"pid":"7115198e29f11f4eebed1adc81c531c2843e98d6","tid":461057,"uid":60524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"跌死佢就岩 我同佢8字唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d09ab3a93545a5423c74087cc1220f04c8f61e","tid":461057,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"馬迷喜訊"},{"pid":"8adb3e1b8d726ecb026a594228f66a1a83c7b757","tid":461057,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"成撚日騎死馬 兄弟們 幫佢地報仇啦"}]}